data.description:
ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT A LOW RATE! This beautiful Forest Ridge section Beverly Hills home may be the one for you! The the first thing you notice when walking in to the living room is that all of the windows are so large to let in the light, and the same can be said for the bonus room in the back. The bonus room is next to the eat in kitchen so it would make a perfect formal living room, or use it to to relax, work or play. The main bedroom has an entire wall of closets for amazing storage, and a step in shower in the ensuite bathroom.
The location is enviable, because its almost smack dab in the the middle of both Lecanto Hwy, which has shopping and restaurants galore, and W Norvell Bryant Hwy which has medical plazas, small stores, and easy access east and west across the county.  Right around the corner are the library and the community park, which are easy to walk to because of the new sidewalks along the main road.
The roof was replaced in 2019, the electrical panel in 2021 and the HVAC in 2020 so you can just move in without a worry! One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged.
